post.title: Enchiladas not Warez
post.content: I seem to have picked up some googles looking for “plus DME crack”. <sigh> When I mentioned “crack” I was talking about my wife’s chicken enchiladas, not piracy. Still, I seem to be in the top 10 sites featuring those words…
